Company Overview
Circadian Zirclight LLC develops light-emitting diode lighting systems which controls .human exposure to spectrum-specific wavelengths for industrial, commercial, and residential applications. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Stoneham, Massachusetts. Circadian Zirclight LLC operates as a subsidiary of Circadian Technologies, Inc.


